data.description: Welcome to your dream home located in a great north Beulah location! With over 3,200 finished sq ft, this home offers a remarkable living experience with its spacious layout, five bedrooms, three baths and two stall heated garage. Situated on a large corner lot, this multi-level home offers plenty of room for entertaining...inside and out! The main level features open concept living plus two bedrooms and full bath. The upper level is a primary suite with stone fireplace, walk-in closet, and private balcony. The lower level offers a family room, 2 bedrooms, bath and large laundry room with storage. Beautiful mature trees and landscaping surround the home including a fenced backyard with two sheds, for storage and heated workshop PLUS BOAT/RV PARKING.
